  <h1>What&#39;s the deal with free energy?</h1>

  

  
    


<div class="article-metadata">

  
  
  
  
  <div>
    

  <span >
      Sun Woo P. Kim</span>
  </div>
  
  

  
  <span class="article-date">
    
    
      
    
    2023-11-16
  </span>
  

  

  

  
  <span class="middot-divider"></span>
